text: Vladimir Alekseyevich Shutov (; born 17 November 1971) is a former Russian football player. Shutov played in the Russian Premier League with FC KAMAZ- Chally Naberezhnye Chelny. ==References== Category:1971 births Category:Living people Category:Soviet footballers Category:Russian footballers Category:FC KAMAZ Naberezhnye Chelny players Category:Russian Premier League players Category:Association football forwards
